comments: Satoransky (CHI) firms up and absorbs the contact from Dinwiddie (BKN) on the dribble hand off.
White (CHI) makes contact to Dinwiddie's (BKN) arm during his shooting motion that affects his jump shot attempt.
Carter Jr. (CHI) establishes himself in a screening position and gives Temple (BKN) room to avoid the contact.
Carter Jr. (CHI) is in the lane for less than three seconds when he receives the pass and shoots.
Carter Jr. (CHI) wraps Jordan (BKN) and the contact affects his ability to receive the pass.
Dinwiddie (BKN) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by White (CHI).
Jordan (BKN) cleanly blocks the shot before he makes incidental leg to leg contact that is initiated by White (CHI).
Carter Jr. (CHI) establishes himself in a screening position and he gives Dinwiddie (BKN) room to avoid the contact.
Jordan (BKN) makes contact to LaVine's (CHI) body during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Dinwiddie (BKN) makes marginal contact with White (CHI) in the backcourt that doesn't affect his ability to defend.
LaVine (CHI) makes marginal contact with Dinwiddie (BKN) and doesn't affect his SQBR.
LaVine (CHI) commits a take foul by grabbing Dinwiddie's (BKN) arm on the perimeter.
Carter Jr. (CHI) firms up in a legal screening position in Harris' (BKN) path and absorbs the contact.
Jordan (BKN) makes incidental contact to LaVine's (CHI) arm after the release that does not affect his ability to follow-through naturally on his jump shot attempt.
LaVine (CHI) briefly engages with Temple (BKN) before he immediately slides off and the contact does not affect his FOM.
Carter Jr. (CHI) establishes himself in a screening position in Temple's (BKN) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
White (CHI) commits a take foul on Dinwiddie (BKN).
Carter Jr. (CHI) commits a take foul on Dinwiddie (BKN).
Dinwiddie (BKN) makes contact with Markkanen's (CHI) body after his release on his jump shot attempt that affects his ability to follow-through naturally.
White (CHI) commits a take foul on Harris (BKN).
Dinwiddie (BKN) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by LaVine (CHI).
Satoransky (CHI) commits a take foul on Temple (BKN).
